                        <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-8">Part 1: <span class="gradient-text">ChatGPT Voice</span></h2>
                        <div class="space-y-8">
                            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
                                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-slate-900">What It Is</h3>
                                <p class="text-slate-700">ChatGPT Voice turns ChatGPT into a conversational partner that can listen and respond in real time. It’s available in the ChatGPT app (iOS, Android, and desktop).</p>
                            </div>
                             <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
                                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-slate-900">Key Features</h3>
                                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-slate-700">
                                    <li>Natural voice conversations with near real-time responses.</li>
                                    <li>Multi-turn dialogue—carry natural back-and-forth without typing.</li>
                                    <li>Cross-device availability (mobile + desktop).</li>
                                    <li>Accessibility—hands-free interaction when typing is not convenient.</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
                                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-slate-900">How to Use</h3>
                                <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-slate-700">
                                    <li>Open the ChatGPT app.</li>
                                    <li>Tap the headphone icon to enter voice mode.</li>
                                    <li>Choose a voice.</li>
                                    <li>Speak naturally, pause to listen, then continue.</li>
                                </ol>
                            </div>
