                    <!-- Section: Part 3 -->
                    <section id="part3" class="content-section">
                        <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-8">Part 3: <span class="gradient-text">Copilot Vision</span></h2>
                        <div class="space-y-8">
                            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
                                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-slate-900">What It Is</h3>
                                <p class="text-slate-700">Copilot Vision is Microsoft’s AI that can see your screen, hear your requests, and guide you interactively. It works in Windows 11 and Edge.</p>
                            </div>
                             <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
                                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-slate-900">Key Features</h3>
                                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-slate-700">
                                    <li>Desktop & App Sharing – AI sees exactly what you see.</li>
                                    <li>Voice Interaction – speak naturally for real-time help.</li>
                                    <li>“Highlights” Guidance – Copilot visually marks where to click or what to edit.</li>
                                    <li>Context-Aware Advice – works across documents, slides, settings, and web pages.</li>
                                    <li>Privacy Control – opt-in only, visuals not stored.</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
                                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-slate-900">How to Use</h3>
                                <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2 text-slate-700">
                                    <li>Open Copilot in Windows or Edge.</li>
                                    <li>Click the eyeglasses icon to enable Vision.</li>
                                    <li>Select a window or your desktop to share.</li>
                                    <li>Speak your request (e.g., “Show me how to adjust slide formatting.”).</li>
                                    <li>Watch Copilot highlight and guide step by step.</li>
                                </ol>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold pt-4 text-slate-900">Practice Activities</h3>
